summary: This code defines a Docker Compose file (version 3) for a service named "vced". It builds the container from context "code" using DockerfileArm and maps ports 8501 and 45679 to the host.

details.comment: This code defines a Docker Compose file (version 3) for a service named "vced". It builds the container from context "code" using DockerfileArm and maps ports 8501 and 45679 to the host.
details.content:
version: "3"
services:
  vced:
    build:
      context: code
      dockerfile: DockerfileArm
    ports:
      - "8501:8501"
      - "45679:45679"
